READ_0700071,《江雪》
千山鳥飛絕，萬徑人蹤滅。
孤舟蓑笠翁，獨釣寒江雪。,《江雪》
千山鸟飞绝，万径人踪灭。
孤舟蓑笠翁，独钓寒江雪。

Items.r: 《江雪》\n千山鳥飛絕，萬徑人蹤滅。\n孤舟蓑笠翁，獨釣寒江雪。

Items.mt: "The Snow in the River" <<\n>>The birds on a thousand mountains fly away, and the people on a thousand paths disappear. <<\n>>A lonely boat with a straw hat, fishing alone in the cold river snow.
